<center><b>What is Poseur?</b></center>

<ul><li>A <i>simple</i> presentation viewer</li></ul>
<ul><li>Written in <b>Python</b> &mdash; using <b>pyglet</b></li></ul>
<ul><li>Free and open source</li></ul>
<ul><li>Supports unicode: זרו ֶ״ֵ</li></ul>


<center><bold>Some features</bold></center>

<ul><li>Write presentations in plain text</li></ul>
<ul><li>Recognizes Markdown-syntax (not yet complete, though)</li></ul>


